## Talks

<div class="talks-container"><div class="talk-card"><div class="talk-header"><div class="talk-type">Invited Talk</div><div class="talk-date">March 15, 2024</div></div><div class="talk-content"><h3 class="talk-title">Mastering Biomedical Data Management</h3><div class="talk-venue"><strong>IFMSA Bangladesh Annual Conference</strong><span class="talk-location">Dhaka, Bangladesh</span></div><p class="talk-description">Comprehensive overview of modern approaches to biomedical data management, including best practices for data collection, storage, and analysis in healthcare research.</p><div class="talk-actions"><a href="talks/mastering-biomedical-data-management/" class="talk-btn" target="_blank">View Slides</a></div></div></div><div class="talk-card"><div class="talk-header"><div class="talk-type">Conference Presentation</div><div class="talk-date">November 8, 2023</div></div><div class="talk-content"><h3 class="talk-title">Machine Learning Applications in Epidemiological Research</h3><div class="talk-venue"><strong>International Conference on Public Health</strong><span class="talk-location">Dhaka, Bangladesh</span></div><p class="talk-description">Exploring the integration of machine learning techniques in epidemiological studies, with focus on disease prediction models and population health analytics.</p></div></div><div class="talk-card"><div class="talk-header"><div class="talk-type">Workshop</div><div class="talk-date">August 25, 2023</div></div><div class="talk-content"><h3 class="talk-title">Open Science and Reproducible Research in Bioinformatics</h3><div class="talk-venue"><strong>Bangladesh Bioinformatics Society</strong><span class="talk-location">Dhaka, Bangladesh</span></div><p class="talk-description">Hands-on workshop on implementing open science practices and ensuring reproducibility in bioinformatics research workflows.</p></div></div><div class="talk-card"><div class="talk-header"><div class="talk-type">Academic Talk</div><div class="talk-date">September 20, 2022</div></div><div class="talk-content"><h3 class="talk-title">State of the Art in Microbial Genome Analysis</h3><div class="talk-venue"><strong>Department of Microbiology, Jagannath University</strong><span class="talk-location">Dhaka, Bangladesh</span></div><p class="talk-description">Latest advances in computational methods for microbial genome analysis, including assembly algorithms, annotation tools, and comparative genomics approaches.</p><div class="talk-actions"><a href="talks/state-the-art-of-microbial-genome-analysi/" class="talk-btn" target="_blank">View Slides</a></div></div></div><div class="talk-card"><div class="talk-header"><div class="talk-type">Invited Talk</div><div class="talk-date">July 10, 2022</div></div><div class="talk-content"><h3 class="talk-title">Undergraduate Research: Importance, Benefits, and Challenges</h3><div class="talk-venue"><strong>CHIRAL Bangladesh Workshop</strong><span class="talk-location">Dhaka, Bangladesh</span></div><p class="talk-description">Exploring the critical role of undergraduate research in academic development, discussing benefits for students and institutions, and addressing common challenges in implementation.</p><div class="talk-actions"><a href="talks/undergraduate-research-importance-benefits-and-challenges/" class="talk-btn" target="_blank">View Slides</a></div></div></div></div>

